    "description": "Netmeds Holdings Services, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Senior Software Engineer for our Tiruchirappalli operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Netmeds Holdings Services:\nNetmeds Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in SQL\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Referral bonus program\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Tiruchirappalli, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Netmeds Holdings Services!",
